#: ../../ai-agent/workflows.md:15
msgid "1. What Is a Workflow?"
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai-agent/workflows.md:17
msgid "A **workflow** is a sequence of typed steps executed by the `lu_ai_workflow` engine. The engine maintains a shared **context** (a JSON dictionary) across all steps — each step can read prior outputs and write its own result back, giving the workflow a persistent memory throughout the run."
msgstr ""

